name: Newborn Hat, Baby Girl, Baby modeling "Her First Bow!"
description:
Infanteeniebeenie.etsy.com & Infanteenie Beenie on Facebook!  

"Infanteenie Beenies" are hats for newborns. Your baby will have the best quality hat during their hopital visit. They will have comfort & style in one bundle! Better yet, all your infants first photos will look amazing.

As a professional photographer, I wanted to combine both the practicality of the hospital hat with a sense of style to create top quality newborn photographs. These infant beenies are sure to enhance any newborn photo!

What I love best about the "Infanteenie Beenies" is the fact that you and all visitors will recognize your baby! 

Each beenie comes delivered in a beautiful package to gift someone you love or to cherish for your soon-to-be bundle of joy.

These make excellent gifts for a soon-to-be mommy or daddy. I send my baby blessings to you or someone you LOVE!
